Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:42.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:97910,102415}I've caught you, St. Tail!\NYou won't get away this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.13,0:01:50.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:109130,110340}Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:52.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111049,112300}Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:01:57.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:113259,117680}So you were the thief, St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.39,0:02:02.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119390,122185}You had me fooled all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:06.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:122727,126606}No, no. I wasn't fooling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:11.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:126814,131569}All this time I just couldn't\Nget myself to tell you the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:17.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:134864,137075}A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:24.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:140870,144123}Ruby, I just can't get myself\Nto tell him…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:30.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147460,150630}…that I'm St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:38.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153966,158930}I definitely can't tell him. And I\Ndefinitely can't let him catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:44.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159764,164936}A FAKE CALLING CARD!?\NTHE SECRET OF THE PERFUME TRAP!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:49.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168606,169941}I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:02:58.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177490,178825}Addressed to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:01.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179033,181828}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:08.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183996,188876}Is it my imagination? Aren't the girls\Nputting extra effort into their hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:11.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189127,191254}Yep. And here's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:17.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191879,197260}A cosmetic company is looking for\Na girl to introduce their new shampoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:22.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197677,202265}Sawatari says that he's taking\Na photo to compete in the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:24.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202515,204058}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:26.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204308,206477}Well, just sit and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:30.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206728,210982}These hands will be sending\Na supermodel into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:35.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211858,215111}Meimi, look this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:39.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215903,219574}Nothing different.\NJust doing his same old stunts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:41.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220116,221868}It's Meimi, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:45.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222118,225538}How can you fight it?\NShe's got beautiful hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:49.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:225872,229959}St. Tail's hair is\Na hundred times prettier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:52.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230168,232503}You don't change either, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:57.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236048,237300}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:04:00.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237550,240470}Speak of the devil!\NIt's a notice from St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:03.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240720,243306}What will it be this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:06.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244265,246893}-Let me have a look!\N-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:13.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247852,253399}"Tomorrow night I will be stealing\Nthe Parfum Takarada Special. -St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:18.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254317,258821}-She's going after some perfume?\N-So that's the next caper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:24.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259071,264827}What's this supposed to mean? I didn 't\Nsend this notice. Who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:31.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268164,271334}Why are you in such deep prayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:36.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273753,276297}You look very depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:40.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276881,280259}I have just lost my father\Nin an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:42.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280843,282887}I'm very sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:45.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283137,285264}My father was a perfumer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:48.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285473,288601}He developed fragrances\Nfor perfumes, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:54.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288851,294273}Yes. Before his death, he mentioned\Na new perfume that was completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:57.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294524,297193}And he was very happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:05:00.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297527,300196}A perfume? Could it be--?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:05.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300446,305660}But just before it was to be completed,\Nhe got into a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:12.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:307995,312166}When Father died, he had\Na notebook clenched in his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:16.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312416,316295}The notebook contained the formula\Nfor his new perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:21.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316504,321092}Your father passionately loved\Nhis work until the very last moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:26.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321342,326597}Yes, but the final ingredient\Nwasn't written in the notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:30.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326848,330893}Now that he's gone,\Nwe don't have any idea what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:34.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331143,334063}Oh, my. You don't have a single clue?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:38.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334605,338317}The last entry in the notebook\Nwas "Earring of Snow."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:41.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:338568,341028}But it was written like a secret code.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:44.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341529,344991}It's probably a flower\Nthat blossoms in the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:49.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346409,349954}Were you in deep prayer trying\Nto find out what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:54.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:350580,354876}Oh, no! I will definitely complete\NFather's perfume on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:57.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355126,357920}That's not what is troubling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:04.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361090,364886}I ask for God's help,\Nfor the sake of my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:06.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365595,366929}Your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:12.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368264,372393}After Father's death, my brother\Nhas become a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:17.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372643,377815}He doesn't care about the perfume,\Nonly about how much he can sell it for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:21.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:378399,381277}He is planning an outrageous scheme!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388826,390494}This is the greenhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:35.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390703,395333}This is where we raise flowers and\Nconcoct ingredients for the perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:41.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396918,401213}And this is the Parfum\NTakarada Special, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:46.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402173,406177}We haven't mass-produced it yet,\Nso this is the only bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:49.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406427,409889}For St. Tail to crave this,\Nshe must see its true value.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:53.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410139,413559}Please leave the security to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:58.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414018,418064}Let's make the security a big thing,\Nas extravagant as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:01.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418648,421776}As extravagant as possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:07.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422234,427698}I'm selling this to a major\Nmanufacturer in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:12.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429116,432703}It would be a disaster\Nif it gets stolen before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:14.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433454,434747}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:19.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435539,439710}In any case, it's a product\Nthat's sure to be a big hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:21.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440503,441712}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:27.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443589,447635}It'll be a smash hit with the help\Nof our little St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:32.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:448386,452056}A St. Tail brand perfume?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:38.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452556,458562}That fake notice was probably sent by\NMiss Takarada's brother to Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:459021,460564}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:46.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461273,466195}He is trying to sell an incomplete\Nperfume formula for a high price…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:51.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466445,471450}…by advertising it as "a perfume\Nworth being stolen by St. Tail."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:53.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471659,473452}What a dirty trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:57.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473661,477081}His sister, Yuriko,\Nsays that she's against…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:08:00.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477331,480960}…sending the incomplete formula\Nout on the market…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:04.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481210,484588}…and deceiving people\Nwith false advertisement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:07.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484839,487425}I'd really like to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:09.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487675,489719}Meimi, you'll do it, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:14.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489927,494724}OK. Let's make the best\Nof that fake calling card!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:20.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496600,500229}Well, now, let's begin\Nour long homeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:22.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500479,502690}Oh, the petals are falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:25.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502940,505776}-What's wrong?\N-The cherry blossoms in the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:28.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506027,508279}Will the flowers hold\Nuntil school is out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:29.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508529,509905}Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:33.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510156,513159}Oh, my goodness. Well, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:39.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513409,519248}We'll have you go out to play in\Nthe yard for this hour of the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:43.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:521042,523711}Just for this hour now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:47.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524545,527923}Really, they're supposed\Nto be junior high students.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:51.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528132,531093}Is it the season\Nor do they just want to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:59.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535556,539685}Sawatari, how could you bring\Nyour camera at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:03.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539935,543481}You amateur, it's in\Nbeautiful scenery like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:06.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543689,546192}…when true beauty\Ncan be photographed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:08.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546442,548360}Hey, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:10.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548569,550529}The same routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:15.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551489,555493}Where's the difference?\NMeimi looks the same to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:20.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:556452,560164}-Meimi, come, come!\N-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:27.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563459,567046}What's wrong with me?\NThat's totally impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:29.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567296,569340}Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:31.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:569799,571926}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:35.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572176,575471}There's something I want\Nto ask you, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:39.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575679,579350}Do you know what the secret code\N"Earring of Snow" means?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:41.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579600,581352}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:45.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581560,585856}Asuka Jr. knows a lot of things.\NHe just might know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:49.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:586565,589652}So winter flowers,\Nwhat kind are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:53.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589902,593489}I don't know anything about flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:10:00.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:595741,600830}There's just one I've heard of.\NWhen I was 5 years old, my mother…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:02.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601080,602206}Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:07.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603332,607503}I think it's a story that\Ngoes back to the Creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:09.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:607878,609130}The Creation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:13.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609672,613092}Well, a story that\Ngoes way back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:19.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615636,619098}Everything in nature\Nhas a color, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:23.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619849,623102}Just as the sky is blue\Nand the clouds are gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:26.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623310,626021}Well, the snow went to see God…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:31.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626522,631443}…and told him, "It's unfair\Nthat I have no color."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:38.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633696,638033}God told the snow, "Ask a flower\Nto give you its color."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:43.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638284,643455}But there wasn't a single flower that\Nwould give the cold snow its color.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:45.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644081,645374}How pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:48.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645624,648752}But, just as the snow was\Nabout to give up…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:53.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649003,653507}…a flower came forth and said,\N"You can have my white color."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:54.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653757,654967}Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:57.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655426,657970}Since then, it's said that…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:11:02.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658220,662600}…the snow protects that small flower\Nduring the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:08.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664351,668355}That's got to be it!\NWhat's the name of that flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:12.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670399,672318}I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:17.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:673569,677281}I know it was\Na delicious-sounding name but…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:21.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678115,681368}Oh, boy! You're hopeless\Nat the crucial moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:23.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682119,683871}Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:41.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:697885,701472}What are you all worked up over?\NIt's just a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:46.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702223,706352}I want to know about the flower\Nthat is able to survive near snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:51.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706602,711899}I can't tell him I'm St. Tail.\NI definitely can't let him catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:55.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713025,715861}Thank you. Forget about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:01.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:717821,721116}What was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:16.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:735589,736882}I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:21.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:738926,741762}Welcome home.\NMeimi, come over here a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:23.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742054,743764}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:29.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745140,749019}-Mother. Mother.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:30.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:749687,750980}Here, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:36.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:751772,756986}Strange. It's not my birthday or our\Nwedding anniversary, but a present?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:757403,759905}Never mind, just open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:50.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767037,770040}What's this? You two are terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:52.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770291,772835}It's my new magic trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:56.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:773085,776797}Oh, you! Just look at this mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:13:00.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777756,780759}What? Snow? Snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:03.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781719,783470}Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:09.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785681,789435}Father, it's a great idea…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:14.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789685,794398}…but isn't it\Na bit off-season for snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:17.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:794606,797735}Maybe you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:23.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798569,803282}Oh! What am I going to do?\NThe dinner has…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:27.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804742,807786}I'm sorry, Eimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:35.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812374,815669}Meimi seemed depressed.\NI was trying to cheer her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:39.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815919,819214}I know. She was moaning\Nin her sleep last night too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:41.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:819465,821717}I wonder if something\Nhappened at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:45.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821967,825554}Don't worry.\NShe's our daughter after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:48.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:825763,828265}She'll get herself back on her feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:50.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:828515,830726}I hope you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:04.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841445,844990}Ruby, well, it's time to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:11.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:846241,851330}I won't, I won't…\NI can't let him catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:16.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852748,856001}Don't worry!\NI'm just fine. I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:25.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:862007,865969}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:32.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:871016,872893}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:36.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874228,876188}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:40.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877564,880442}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:58.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893914,898127}Meimi, the flower that\NAsuka Jr. was talking about…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:15:01.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898377,901296}…it's probably called the snow drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:03.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:901547,903132}How did you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:08.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:903882,908554}It's the only winter flower\Nthat has a delicious-sounding name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:11.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:909054,911557}I see! Thanks, Seira!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:17.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:913851,917563}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:28.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925070,928740}The perfume in Mr. Takarada's hand\Nis St. Tail's target.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:33.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:928991,933662}-Let's keep the security tight.\N-Yes, Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:40.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934663,940461}With this security alone, St. Tail\Nwill be associated with this perfume…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:46.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:940711,946300}…even if the notice is fake\Nand St. Tail doesn't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:51.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946800,951430}-Asuka Jr., this woman.\N-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:54.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951889,954099}Yuriko! I told you to get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:58.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:954641,958061}Brother, please stop all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:03.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961440,963025}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:07.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:964401,967488}Good evening!\NThank you for the invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:12.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968697,972701}-Invitation?\N-This can't be! The notice is a--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:16.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973535,976663}-Something wrong with the notice?\N-Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:20.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977831,980626}Why is the real St. Tail here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:24.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981210,984129}I'm the one that sent\Nthe fake calling card out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:29.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986131,989051}- Darn it!\N-Brother, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.51,0:16:32.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989510,992262}You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:40.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994973,1000229}God sees through everything!\NOne! Two! Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:53.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011907,1013825}Hold it! That's--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:17:00.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017371,1020958}-I'm leaving with the perfume!\N-Hold it, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:05.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021208,1025295}Who will let you get away with it?\NWait! Give that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:07.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025546,1027381}There you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:16.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032427,1036557}Asuka Jr., the perfume!\NGet that perfume back for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:20.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037391,1040894}Mr. Takarada, it's time\Nfor you to wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:24.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041103,1044273}What's going on here, St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:32.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050153,1052030}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:35.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052948,1055450}…Show…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:38.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056618,1058787}…Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:47.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065961,1067713}Asuka Jr., this is…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:52.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068130,1072676}What's happening?\NThe temperature is-- It's snowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:55.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072926,1075095}Is it her famous illusion trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:18:01.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076013,1081977}Stop! Father's flowers will die! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:08.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082227,1088650}If the flowers die, we won't be able\Nto make the perfume! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:16.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090485,1096199}Brother, it's your fault. If Father's\Nflowers die, it's all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:23.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100454,1103165}Yuriko, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:26.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105125,1106710}Yuriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:31.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107669,1111340}You two will be able\Nto make a wonderful perfume…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:34.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111590,1114051}…even without the use of my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:37.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114885,1117971}What are you blabbering about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:41.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118805,1121975}Let's forget about it, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:44.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122392,1124936}But the perfume…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:50.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125479,1130233}That calling card, I was the one\Nwho sent it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:56.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130942,1136698}Instead of completing the perfume,\Nall I thought of was how to sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:19:01.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137199,1141662}If St. Tail was after it, it would\Nbecome famous. That's why I…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141912,1143330}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:08.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143580,1148669}Asuka Jr., I should have gone\Nand told you of it sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:14.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153423,1154549}Snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:20.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157219,1160430}No, they're white flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:30.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167312,1170357}The fragrance of this flower,\Ncould it be…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:35.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170732,1175320}The final ingredient in the notebook,\N"Earring of Snow," is this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:38.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175737,1178365}We can make it! Father's perfume!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:41.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178615,1181493}Yuriko, let's try\Nto complete it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:42.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181702,1182703}Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:50.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186873,1190877}St. Tail, come down here\Nand challenge me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:55.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192421,1195090}You had me fooled all along,\Ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:57.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195340,1197551}I didn't mean to fool you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:03.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198135,1203473}I can't say it with words.\NI can't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:08.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205350,1208520}Asuka Jr., I'm sorry\Nto have troubled you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:13.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208770,1213859}I'm glad it was stolen.\NSt. Tail has helped me to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:16.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214443,1216820}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:31.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225287,1231460}This puts me on the spot.\NAll because of St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:44.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240886,1244848}No, not yet.\NI can't afford to get caught yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:48.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245932,1248393}I can't get caught.
